'''Margath's on Elshandruu Pica''' was a conglomerate of [[Cantina|bars]], [[Casino/Legends|casinos]], and restaurants owned and operated by [[Kina Margath]] on [[Elshandruu Pica]] in the city of [[Picavil]]. Among the various places for relaxation, gambling, drinking, and dining was the five-star rated [[27th Hour Social Club]]. Another branch was located in [[Vlarnya]] on [[Courkrus]].

